yacl3.config.earthy:config.server.desc: The name of the server to be used in API requests, do not change this unless there is a server reset or you will probably break things
yacl3.config.earthy:config.showAffiliati: If enabled, players will have their town and nation displayed above their head
yacl3.config.earthy:config.previewCurren: If enabled, your chat box will show a preview of the current channel you are part of when empty
yacl3.config.earthy:config.autoHUD.desc: Automatically enable a Towny HUD type on connection to EarthMC
